---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Yati"
  description="About Yatheendra KV — engineer, watch enthusiast, and curious thinker writing on horology, software, philosophy, sports, film and more."
>
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="avatar-wrap">
      <img src="/avatar.jpg" alt="Yati" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
    </div>
    <div class="about-intro">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>Yatheendra KV</h1>
      <p class="tagline">Engineer · Watch enthusiast · Curious thinker</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="about-body">
    <p>
      I'm an engineer by trade and a generalist by temperament. This is my corner of
      the internet — a place to think out loud about the things I keep coming back to.
    </p>
    <p>
      I write about horology and the craft of watchmaking, software and how it's made,
      philosophy and the questions that won't go away, plus the books, films and sport
      that fill the rest of my time. No agenda, no content calendar — just honest writing
      on whatever's on my mind.
    </p>

    <h2>What you'll find here</h2>
    <p>
      Essays and notes that range from the mechanical poetry of an automatic movement to
      the discipline of good code, from arguments I'm still having with myself to the
      occasional thought about God. If any of that sounds like your kind of thing, the
      <a href="/blog">writing</a> is the best place to start.
    </p>

    <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
    <div class="social-links">
      <a href="https://github.com/yatheendra72" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://x.com/yatheendra72" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/yatikv" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="mailto:yatheendra72@gmail.com">Email</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.75rem;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    padding: 2.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .avatar-wrap { flex-shrink: 0; }

  .avatar-wrap img {
    width: 128px;
    height: 128px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    border: 3px solid var(--card-bg);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--accent), var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
  }

  h1 { margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }

  .tagline {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .about-body {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.07rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .about-body p { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

  .about-body h2 {
    margin: 2.5rem 0 0.85rem;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }

  .about-body a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: transparent;
    transition: text-decoration-color var(--transition);
  }

  .about-body a:hover { text-decoration-color: var(--accent); }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
    font-family: var(--sans);
  }

  .social-links a {
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--muted);
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color var(--transition), border-color var(--transition),
      background var(--transition), transform var(--transition);
  }

  .social-links a:hover {
    color: var(--on-accent);
    background: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .about-hero {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.75rem;
    }
    .social-links { justify-content: center; }
  }
</style>
